WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 31=

01:46.420 --> 01:47.420
- Good!
- Go on!

01:47.420 --> 01:48.260
Nice!

01:48.990 --> 01:49.830
Block him!

01:55.550 --> 01:56.390
Great pass!

02:00.910 --> 02:01.750
Amazing!

02:02.990 --> 02:03.830
He caught that too?

02:04.140 --> 02:05.550
Charge! Charge!

02:06.910 --> 02:08.230
- Charge!
- Go!

02:08.230 --> 02:09.390
That was so fast!

02:12.550 --> 02:13.670
It's in!

02:13.670 --> 02:14.990
Well done!

02:15.180 --> 02:17.350
- Good!
- Good!

02:17.580 --> 02:19.140
- Good!
- Good!

02:28.550 --> 02:30.620
- Good!
- Good!

02:37.180 --> 02:38.020
Good!

02:44.350 --> 02:45.390
Wonderful!

02:56.140 --> 02:56.980
It's in!

02:57.230 --> 02:58.740
Well done!

02:59.070 --> 02:59.910
- Good!
- Good!

03:04.510 --> 03:05.700
Nice teamwork.

03:05.990 --> 03:06.830
Keep going.

03:08.230 --> 03:09.070
Meng Wan,

03:10.140 --> 03:10.980
I like you.

03:12.110 --> 03:13.580
I know. I like you too.

03:13.740 --> 03:14.580
Let's go play.

03:14.580 --> 03:15.420
Meng Wan,

03:16.110 --> 03:16.950
I'm serious.

03:17.300 --> 03:18.790
I wanted to tell you in Liangzhou.

03:21.880 --> 03:24.810
♪My wish might be♪

03:26.950 --> 03:28.020
The match isn't over yet.

03:30.990 --> 03:31.900
When it's over,

03:32.790 --> 03:33.630
I'll wait for you.

03:36.820 --> 03:40.420
♪I hate that I hesitated♪

03:40.840 --> 03:44.380
♪And didn't dare draw near again♪

03:44.670 --> 03:47.330
♪Leaving all behind♪

03:47.610 --> 03:52.050
♪The sudden pause of words unsaid♪

03:52.360 --> 03:55.840
♪How I long to hold
that silhouette close♪

03:56.270 --> 03:59.920
♪After waking up, we walk back-to-back♪

04:00.150 --> 04:08.270
♪Watching all that is unfinished
fade away♪

04:19.343 --> 04:20.979
- The horse is startled!
- It's startled!

04:20.990 --> 04:21.910
The horse is startled!

04:22.380 --> 04:23.940
Watch out!

04:24.150 --> 04:25.030
Move aside!

04:25.380 --> 04:26.260
Move!

04:59.740 --> 05:00.710
That was dangerous.

05:00.860 --> 05:01.700
Exactly.

05:21.860 --> 05:25.720
♪I hate that I hesitated♪

05:27.030 --> 05:28.180
Is your back stronger

05:28.180 --> 05:29.030
than a horse's hooves?

05:29.743 --> 05:30.623
You're only a scholar.

05:30.940 --> 05:31.780
Don't push yourself.

05:32.600 --> 05:36.540
♪The sudden pause of words unsaid♪

05:36.620 --> 05:37.460
Are you alright?

05:39.420 --> 05:40.260
I'm fine.

05:41.350 --> 05:44.990
♪After waking up, we walk back-to-back♪

05:45.260 --> 05:46.740
Thank you for saving me, Mr. Fang.

05:47.010 --> 05:53.610
♪All that is unfinished fade away♪

06:07.150 --> 06:07.990
I am fine.

06:08.940 --> 06:09.973
I'll go get some medicine.

06:11.380 --> 06:12.350
Thank you, Miss He.

06:12.410 --> 06:15.770
♪Let memories drift away♪

06:16.180 --> 06:18.880
♪Alone, I gather them up♪

06:19.080 --> 06:23.440
♪Like petals in the spring sun♪

06:23.850 --> 06:27.530
♪Till the past falls still again♪

06:27.770 --> 06:31.310
♪And turns to clear daylight♪

06:31.540 --> 06:39.620
♪The wind returns with my dreams♪

06:41.670 --> 06:42.510
Miss Duan.

06:44.230 --> 06:45.120
Miss Duan,

06:45.120 --> 06:46.160
you must've been scared.

06:47.260 --> 06:48.710
This is a Calming Pill

06:49.550 --> 06:50.670
to settle your nerves.

06:53.990 --> 06:54.860
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

06:55.940 --> 06:57.030
You're too polite.

07:02.420 --> 07:04.110
Since our families are now joined,

07:04.910 --> 07:06.470
we'll be one family.

07:06.790 --> 07:08.060
We should get to know

07:08.060 --> 07:08.910
each other better.

07:08.910 --> 07:09.750
We may grow

07:09.760 --> 07:10.860
even closer, right?

07:11.910 --> 07:12.770
Mr. Wang,

07:12.780 --> 07:13.790
please mind your manners.

07:14.380 --> 07:15.220
Miss Duan,

07:15.590 --> 07:17.030
when you dodged that wild horse,

07:17.030 --> 07:18.030
you dropped something.

07:18.420 --> 07:19.350
If it is convenient,

07:19.710 --> 07:20.590
I can bring it to you.

07:23.550 --> 07:24.790
How could I trouble you?

07:25.060 --> 07:26.180
I will fetch it myself.

07:26.860 --> 07:27.700
This way, please.

07:38.590 --> 07:39.710
The Duan clan is full

07:39.710 --> 07:40.820
of beauties.

07:41.940 --> 07:43.300
Pretty, who are you?

07:43.300 --> 07:44.570
- Get lost.
- You...

07:57.420 --> 07:58.260
Mr. Fang,

07:59.180 --> 08:00.790
what was it that I dropped earlier?

08:03.350 --> 08:04.940
That was just a lie I made up.

08:06.230 --> 08:07.670
I didn't see you drop anything.

08:08.550 --> 08:10.190
I only saw you uneasy,

08:10.670 --> 08:11.510
so I thought

08:11.800 --> 08:12.640
perhaps you needed

08:12.640 --> 08:13.620
an excuse to step away.

08:17.500 --> 08:19.470
What makes you think I was uneasy?

08:20.420 --> 08:21.500
Weren't you about to cry?

08:23.710 --> 08:24.550
Cry?

08:25.030 --> 08:25.870
Here.

08:27.550 --> 08:28.390
Here?

08:36.830 --> 08:37.950
Look closely.

08:38.470 --> 08:40.020
This one is tear makeup.

08:40.380 --> 08:42.190
It's the latest fashion.

08:42.350 --> 08:43.500
I'm not about to cry.

08:43.950 --> 08:44.790
Look.

09:02.110 --> 09:03.020
Why make yourself

09:03.620 --> 09:05.110
look like you're about to cry?

09:05.990 --> 09:06.830
A smile

09:07.070 --> 09:08.430
is far better than tears,

09:08.950 --> 09:09.790
isn't it?

09:12.430 --> 09:13.620
What would you know?

09:14.190 --> 09:15.030
This kind of makeup

09:15.380 --> 09:16.540
creates a frail,

09:16.540 --> 09:18.140
pitiful look.

09:19.190 --> 09:20.310
I don't get it.

09:21.590 --> 09:22.660
I always thought

09:22.860 --> 09:23.990
a lady so radiant

09:23.990 --> 09:25.310
as you

09:25.590 --> 09:26.830
would never need pity.

10:10.070 --> 10:10.910
Mr. Fang,

10:11.860 --> 10:13.380
you are better as yourself.

10:14.660 --> 10:16.110
You need not imitate Xu.

10:30.540 --> 10:31.470
Miss He.

10:41.860 --> 10:42.740
He is fond of you.

10:44.900 --> 10:46.960
Miss He, don't jest. I...

10:46.970 --> 10:48.380
When the horse was startled,

10:48.590 --> 10:49.710
everyone else ran away.

10:50.140 --> 10:51.380
Only he rushed over at once

10:51.380 --> 10:52.260
to shield you.

10:52.260 --> 10:53.860
He nearly got badly hurt for it.

10:54.950 --> 10:55.830
If you ask me,

10:55.830 --> 10:56.780
seeing him like this,

10:57.540 --> 10:58.380
I think he'd even die

10:58.590 --> 10:59.430
for you

10:59.590 --> 11:00.470
willingly.

11:01.500 --> 11:02.350
Good. Well passed.

11:02.780 --> 11:04.540
- Good.
- Nice.

11:05.260 --> 11:07.900
- Good.
- Good.

11:08.070 --> 11:08.910
Impressive.

11:11.230 --> 11:12.430
Nice shot.

11:13.500 --> 11:15.260
Xu, well done.

11:32.020 --> 11:34.140
(Though she's from the jianghu,)

11:34.710 --> 11:36.740
(she'd make a fine sister-in-law.)

12:09.620 --> 12:10.900
What are you doing?

12:12.830 --> 12:13.710
I meant what I said.

12:15.260 --> 12:16.100
I like you.

12:22.470 --> 12:23.590
After we returned to Nandu,

12:24.141 --> 12:25.805
each time I heard
about your blind dates,

12:25.816 --> 12:26.936
I'd feel anxious and upset.

12:28.020 --> 12:29.533
Anxious that you'd say yes to another.

12:29.950 --> 12:31.110
Upset with myself.

12:32.260 --> 12:33.380
I'd liked you for so long,

12:34.070 --> 12:35.270
yet I didn't dare to tell you.

12:36.590 --> 12:37.430
Meng Wan,

12:38.350 --> 12:39.540
I've made up my mind today.

12:40.900 --> 12:41.900
I have to tell you.

12:43.740 --> 12:44.580
Well...

12:44.860 --> 12:45.700
Meng Wan.

12:48.140 --> 12:49.260
What do you like about me?

12:51.020 --> 12:51.860
I can't quite say.

12:53.230 --> 12:54.190
But I just like you.

12:55.190 --> 12:56.110
You can't even say

12:56.110 --> 12:57.070
what you like about me.

12:57.070 --> 12:58.070
Why should I believe you?

12:58.110 --> 12:59.049
If I can say it clearly,

12:59.060 --> 12:59.900
would you accept me?

13:00.110 --> 13:00.950
Who said that?

13:03.260 --> 13:04.100
Meng Wan,

13:07.310 --> 13:08.430
I truly like you.

13:10.540 --> 13:12.310
I like you for having principles,

13:13.740 --> 13:14.830
being strong-willed,

13:16.590 --> 13:18.070
always following your heart,

13:18.830 --> 13:19.860
and acting with resolve.

13:22.830 --> 13:23.670
I also like you

13:24.020 --> 13:24.900
for never shrinking

13:25.990 --> 13:26.950
before the foe.

13:28.380 --> 13:29.326
Surely, I also like you

13:30.260 --> 13:31.430
for being good-looking.

13:34.830 --> 13:35.670
All right.

13:36.140 --> 13:36.980
I hear you.

13:38.740 --> 13:39.780
What do you mean

13:40.470 --> 13:41.590
by that?

13:42.190 --> 13:43.310
It means I heard you.

13:43.900 --> 13:44.740
Then...

13:45.110 --> 13:46.140
Does that mean you agree?

13:46.140 --> 13:46.990
I never said that.

13:48.430 --> 13:49.950
Then what do you mean? Be clear.

13:49.950 --> 13:51.110
Why do you ask so much?

13:51.540 --> 13:52.590
All right? I hear you?

14:04.950 --> 14:06.230
Do you like how I look today?

14:07.780 --> 14:08.620
Not bad.

14:09.110 --> 14:10.540
Flames blaze; banners fly high.

14:10.860 --> 14:12.260
A young man rides wild and free.

14:15.500 --> 14:16.350
Good that you like it.

14:18.380 --> 14:19.310
I wanted you to see

14:19.540 --> 14:20.500
the vigor in this world

14:21.230 --> 14:22.140
and the truest,

14:24.070 --> 14:25.020
brightest me.

14:25.860 --> 14:27.230
I saw through you

14:27.590 --> 14:28.830
long ago.

14:56.740 --> 14:58.260
Ten days pass quickly.

14:59.660 --> 15:00.950
Time really flies.

15:02.500 --> 15:03.340
Simu,

15:05.350 --> 15:06.710
how does the Mortal World feel now?

15:13.540 --> 15:14.740
This world

15:20.500 --> 15:22.230
is truly a vivid painted scroll.

15:47.170 --> 15:48.020
What a fine tune.

15:48.020 --> 15:48.860
Yes.

15:49.590 --> 15:50.430
Wonderful.

16:01.590 --> 16:02.830
- Wonderful.
- A fine tune.

16:02.830 --> 16:03.710
Truly exquisite.

16:03.710 --> 16:04.740
Luoxian's Qin skill

16:04.740 --> 16:05.620
is truly remarkable.

16:05.830 --> 16:07.070
- Indeed.
- Splendid.

16:07.260 --> 16:08.100
Yes.

16:09.140 --> 16:09.980
Come.

16:10.540 --> 16:11.990
Today, you seem

16:11.990 --> 16:12.990
especially radiant

16:13.190 --> 16:14.140
in quite fine spirits.

16:14.140 --> 16:14.980
Do I?

16:16.110 --> 16:17.070
You must be mistaken.

16:18.710 --> 16:19.740
It's already the Hai hour.

16:20.310 --> 16:21.620
Your shift ended long ago.

16:21.620 --> 16:22.460
One more cup.

16:22.590 --> 16:23.710
Go back and get some rest.

16:24.470 --> 16:25.310
- But
- Cheers.

16:25.620 --> 16:26.660
you still have guests.

16:27.170 --> 16:28.010
Cheers.

16:28.860 --> 16:29.860
An exception for today.

16:31.470 --> 16:32.830
Let everyone here

16:33.660 --> 16:34.950
leave fully satisfied.

16:34.950 --> 16:35.910
Lately, in Nandu,

16:35.910 --> 16:36.950
any curious tales?

16:37.470 --> 16:38.740
The biggest tale

16:39.140 --> 16:40.610
is about Wang Jin, right?

16:40.830 --> 16:41.251
I heard

16:41.262 --> 16:42.926
the Vice Minister
of the Judicial Review,

16:42.937 --> 16:43.760
Wang Jin,

16:43.760 --> 16:44.950
is actually a prince.

16:46.740 --> 16:47.860
It's too late now.

16:48.110 --> 16:49.430
He's now a prince

16:49.720 --> 16:51.140
and not easy to meet.

16:51.470 --> 16:52.400
Come, Wang.

16:52.900 --> 16:53.740
Let's just drink

16:53.900 --> 16:55.660
and enjoy the songs.

17:00.950 --> 17:01.900
Splendid indeed.

17:16.430 --> 17:17.270
I finally made it.

17:18.540 --> 17:19.500
Given your identity,

17:19.740 --> 17:20.630
you needn't come.

17:20.990 --> 17:21.830
It's all right.

17:21.990 --> 17:23.150
The guards are posted nearby.

17:23.640 --> 17:24.500
Fang Ji,

17:24.500 --> 17:25.189
you and Luoxian

17:25.200 --> 17:26.340
should take care on the way

17:26.351 --> 17:27.280
to Yunzhou and Luozhou.

17:37.780 --> 17:38.620
Stay alert.

17:42.230 --> 17:43.070
Fang Ji,

17:44.500 --> 17:45.630
we will meet again someday.

18:07.430 --> 18:08.270
Just as you expected,

18:08.820 --> 18:09.780
His Majesty is pleased

18:09.780 --> 18:11.150
with the manuscript

18:12.506 --> 18:13.572
about Tianluo purification.

18:14.340 --> 18:16.300
Now, Luoxian is a Commandery Princess,

18:16.670 --> 18:18.670
sent to Luozhou as an instructor.

18:19.230 --> 18:20.990
That will make things much easier.

18:21.500 --> 18:22.820
Luoxian once promised me

18:22.990 --> 18:24.230
to build another Wensheng Agency

18:24.630 --> 18:25.823
in Yunzhou and Luozhou for us.

18:26.260 --> 18:27.703
That will make Fang Ji's work there

18:27.990 --> 18:28.870
much easier.

18:29.190 --> 18:31.060
As Luozhou's Vice Commissioner,

18:31.693 --> 18:32.773
Fang Ji will open the mines

18:33.020 --> 18:34.230
once he arrives.

18:36.500 --> 18:37.950
Lately, Chong's strife has eased.

18:38.190 --> 18:39.470
They keep stirring at our border.

18:39.740 --> 18:40.950
It's time for me to head north.

18:41.630 --> 18:42.656
After Fang Ji and I leave,

18:43.390 --> 18:44.300
the troublesome Nandu

18:44.470 --> 18:45.369
will be in your hands.

18:47.060 --> 18:47.900
Rest easy.

18:48.430 --> 18:49.870
Though our armor is strong

18:50.397 --> 18:51.410
and our horses are robust,

18:51.680 --> 18:52.836
our cavalry still can't match

18:52.847 --> 18:54.767
the Chong people,
who were raised on horseback.

18:55.020 --> 18:55.990
You must find a way

18:56.150 --> 18:57.150
to check their cavalry.

18:58.300 --> 18:59.140
We seized

18:59.300 --> 19:00.340
the three prefectures

19:00.760 --> 19:01.833
while Chong was in turmoil.

19:03.300 --> 19:04.150
Nothing will come

19:04.150 --> 19:05.150
that easily again.

19:06.190 --> 19:07.223
We must be fully prepared.

19:07.710 --> 19:08.740
General Duan, how long

19:09.300 --> 19:10.340
should this war go on?

19:12.470 --> 19:13.310
As the saying goes,

19:13.615 --> 19:14.831
five victories bring calamity;

19:14.842 --> 19:15.936
four victories bring costs;

19:15.947 --> 19:17.270
three victories bring domination.

19:17.543 --> 19:18.709
If the war drags on too long,

19:18.870 --> 19:20.340
the people and treasury will break.

19:22.670 --> 19:23.510
Three campaigns

19:24.230 --> 19:25.390
to reclaim our lost land

19:26.190 --> 19:27.030
would be perfect.

19:28.260 --> 19:29.100
Three?

19:30.230 --> 19:31.070
General Duan,

19:31.340 --> 19:32.780
your plan is truly bold.

19:33.230 --> 19:34.190
Still,

19:34.190 --> 19:35.710
it does suit your style.

19:45.620 --> 19:48.940
(Lotusborn Pavilion)

19:54.540 --> 19:55.380
Everything is ready.

19:55.740 --> 19:56.580
Great Ancestor,

19:56.580 --> 19:57.460
let us begin at once.

20:47.220 --> 20:48.429
I've refined this soul candle

20:48.440 --> 20:49.540
into this bracelet.

20:50.150 --> 20:51.740
Whoever holds this bracelet

20:52.230 --> 20:53.340
will control the master

20:53.340 --> 20:54.540
of this soul candle.

20:55.670 --> 20:56.510
Great Ancestor,

20:57.300 --> 20:58.260
the bracelet is done.

20:58.990 --> 21:02.060
Are you returning to the Void?

21:13.150 --> 21:14.200
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

21:19.990 --> 21:21.060
Escorting this lad

21:21.630 --> 21:22.780
has worn me out on the road.

21:24.100 --> 21:24.940
Yes.

21:27.580 --> 21:28.990
Camping rough day after day.

21:46.820 --> 21:47.910
Still dreaming

21:47.910 --> 21:48.780
of becoming a Priest?

21:50.390 --> 21:52.710
Hiding a sacred robe is a capital crime.

21:53.360 --> 21:54.220
Your post as Priest

21:54.220 --> 21:55.280
has already been stripped.

21:55.630 --> 21:56.710
Why do you need that?

21:58.780 --> 22:00.390
Give it back. Give it back!

22:00.390 --> 22:01.230
That is mine.

22:03.630 --> 22:04.500
Give it to me.

22:10.990 --> 22:11.830
Give it to me.

22:12.540 --> 22:13.380
Give…

23:01.540 --> 23:02.710
How dare you glare at me?

23:02.950 --> 23:04.020
Who do you think you are?

23:04.880 --> 23:05.740
I...

23:05.740 --> 23:06.580
- Die!
- Calm down.

23:06.740 --> 23:07.580
I...

23:07.820 --> 23:08.660
Move aside.

23:32.870 --> 23:34.670
I didn't mean to.

23:36.470 --> 23:37.310
I...

23:39.630 --> 23:40.540
I'll kill you.

23:51.580 --> 23:52.630
I knew

23:53.540 --> 23:54.780
you'd need me.

23:59.870 --> 24:00.780
Evil spirit,

24:01.390 --> 24:02.230
leave at once.

24:05.340 --> 24:06.470
If I leave,

24:08.430 --> 24:09.630
you'll die by the blade

24:09.630 --> 24:12.020
of some nameless foot soldier.

24:17.670 --> 24:18.670
Can you accept that?

24:20.540 --> 24:21.430
You are North Chong's

24:21.430 --> 24:23.230
most gifted Young Priest.

24:23.710 --> 24:25.990
Your faith is truer than anyone's.

24:26.430 --> 24:27.500
You want all under heaven

24:27.500 --> 24:29.150
to follow your faith.

24:31.260 --> 24:33.340
It was people like Duan Xu

24:33.660 --> 24:34.500
and the High Priest

24:34.500 --> 24:36.500
who drove you to this end.

24:36.870 --> 24:38.100
Your heart is full

24:38.100 --> 24:39.470
of rage and unwillingness.

24:40.500 --> 24:41.710
Yet you would still die

24:41.710 --> 24:43.100
such a lowly death.

24:47.230 --> 24:48.910
If you become the High Priest,

24:49.740 --> 24:51.430
you won't only live,

24:52.670 --> 24:54.390
but you can fulfill your long wish

24:55.740 --> 24:57.820
and seize your own fate.

25:01.340 --> 25:03.950
Seize my own fate?

25:11.020 --> 25:12.710
That is the way of this world.

25:13.780 --> 25:14.820
If you don't kill them,

25:15.740 --> 25:17.230
they will come for your life.

25:18.150 --> 25:18.990
Why me?

25:19.910 --> 25:21.020
Why must it be me?

25:21.630 --> 25:22.820
Your soul is pure and true.

25:22.820 --> 25:24.390
You are fated for the Spirit World.

25:27.170 --> 25:28.020
They fear

25:28.020 --> 25:29.540
that you may gain greater power,

25:29.670 --> 25:31.190
so they mean to kill you.

25:35.300 --> 25:36.140
Impossible.

25:36.710 --> 25:37.550
No way.

25:38.500 --> 25:39.430
You're lying to me.

25:39.430 --> 25:40.580
Everyone in this world

25:40.580 --> 25:41.740
is waiting for you to die.

25:46.340 --> 25:47.470
Only I

25:48.780 --> 25:50.300
will keep you alive.

25:52.250 --> 25:53.100
I will make you

25:53.100 --> 25:54.820
become the High Priest.

26:25.780 --> 26:27.190
I am Yan Ke.

26:27.740 --> 26:28.870
When you call for me again,

26:29.390 --> 26:30.780
remember my name.

26:51.340 --> 26:54.060
(Yueran Fragrance)

27:00.580 --> 27:02.430
The new master's fragrance craft

27:02.820 --> 27:03.990
is far below Master Xuan's.

27:11.580 --> 27:12.420
Milady.

27:14.020 --> 27:14.860
Milady?

28:04.100 --> 28:06.230
You're just a frail girl on Mafeisan.

28:06.230 --> 28:08.060
Let's see how you can fight back now.

28:12.630 --> 28:14.060
Being tied up is no fun.

28:14.190 --> 28:15.820
Come on, I'll untie you.

28:16.100 --> 28:17.190
What are you doing, Wang Qi?

28:18.020 --> 28:18.910
I'm warning you.

28:19.630 --> 28:21.100
I am a Duan legitimate daughter.

28:21.630 --> 28:23.060
If you dare lay a hand on me,

28:23.340 --> 28:24.430
my father and brother

28:24.430 --> 28:25.670
will never let you off.

28:26.230 --> 28:27.300
I know.

28:27.820 --> 28:29.780
You're the pearl of your family.

28:29.910 --> 28:31.820
So proud and aloof.

28:31.919 --> 28:33.585
But my father is
the Minister of Revenue.

28:33.596 --> 28:34.780
Yet you kept brushing me off.

28:34.780 --> 28:35.710
You even slighted me

28:35.710 --> 28:36.550
before Fang Xianye.

28:36.550 --> 28:37.910
What is Fang Xianye, anyway?

28:37.910 --> 28:40.500
A lowborn stray with no kin or name.

28:42.020 --> 28:42.860
Shame on you.

28:53.580 --> 28:55.390
Do you really think

28:55.710 --> 28:56.630
your father and brother

28:56.630 --> 28:57.710
can do anything to me?

29:00.470 --> 29:01.990
Let me tell you the truth.

29:02.580 --> 29:05.190
Once we have consummated relations,

29:06.500 --> 29:08.230
for the sake of your good name,

29:08.470 --> 29:10.390
your family will marry you to me.

29:10.950 --> 29:12.150
When that time comes…

29:14.870 --> 29:16.300
Just thinking of it delights me.

29:18.260 --> 29:19.470
Duan Shunxi.

29:20.500 --> 29:21.820
The mere thought of him angers me.

29:22.500 --> 29:23.580
Because of him, my sister

29:23.950 --> 29:25.150
is still missing.

29:26.990 --> 29:28.100
Your family owes us.

29:29.150 --> 29:31.100
How will you repay that debt?

29:33.190 --> 29:34.060
Come on.

29:35.020 --> 29:36.300
How dare you

29:36.300 --> 29:37.710
press me on this?

29:38.740 --> 29:39.950
Come on, yield to me.

29:40.100 --> 29:41.340
Now, take off your clothes.

29:42.820 --> 29:43.660
Don't touch me.

29:45.500 --> 29:46.670
See? We're getting closer.

29:48.710 --> 29:50.800
- Help!
- Come on.

29:50.810 --> 29:51.670
Yes, just like that.

29:51.670 --> 29:52.780
Help!

29:54.720 --> 29:55.560
Don't struggle.

29:55.580 --> 29:56.420
Don't touch me.

29:56.910 --> 29:57.820
Don't touch me.

30:00.060 --> 30:01.390
Let me go.

30:47.740 --> 30:48.580
What's wrong?

30:49.470 --> 30:51.190
Weren't you enjoying yourself?

30:52.060 --> 30:52.910
Leaving so soon?

30:53.540 --> 30:57.020
You're the one…

31:05.540 --> 31:06.670
How shall we deal with him?

31:10.870 --> 31:11.910
Shall we kill him?

31:23.870 --> 31:24.710
No.

31:25.300 --> 31:26.140
No.

31:27.630 --> 31:28.470
No.

31:28.990 --> 31:29.830
No.

31:34.540 --> 31:35.630
There are better ways

31:36.630 --> 31:38.500
to torment a man.

31:50.630 --> 31:51.470
Fangcao,

31:51.820 --> 31:52.660
don't come closer.

31:53.340 --> 31:55.580
Fangcao, Biyun, stay back.

31:56.100 --> 31:56.940
Don't come for me.

31:59.230 --> 32:00.430
Biyun, don't come closer.

32:00.820 --> 32:02.540
Xiang, don't come near me.

32:02.870 --> 32:04.100
I didn't kill you.

32:04.100 --> 32:05.260
If I were found out…

32:05.710 --> 32:06.780
Don't come near me.

32:13.230 --> 32:14.300
A ghost!

32:15.910 --> 32:16.870
Ghost!

32:18.150 --> 32:18.990
He...

32:19.670 --> 32:21.060
What's wrong with him?

32:21.300 --> 32:23.150
He's trapped in ten days in an illusion.

32:23.710 --> 32:24.910
Once he comes to his senses,

32:25.410 --> 32:26.990
he likely won't go near women.

32:35.820 --> 32:36.660
You...

32:38.060 --> 32:39.580
Who exactly are you?

32:44.470 --> 32:45.310
He Simu.

33:10.540 --> 33:11.430
Miss He.

33:13.990 --> 33:14.830
Thank…

33:15.230 --> 33:16.300
Thank you.

33:18.900 --> 33:22.300
(Duan Mansion)

33:36.020 --> 33:37.540
Simu dealt with Wang Qi for you.

33:45.740 --> 33:47.230
You knew all along

33:47.910 --> 33:48.990
that Miss He is a spirit?

33:50.060 --> 33:50.900
I knew.

33:52.710 --> 33:53.910
And you still care for her?

33:54.150 --> 33:55.670
You still want to be with her?

33:58.950 --> 33:59.790
Jingyuan,

34:01.060 --> 34:02.470
I know you're thinking of me.

34:04.630 --> 34:05.740
You're my only sister.

34:07.060 --> 34:08.390
You want me to be happy,

34:10.220 --> 34:11.060
don't you?

34:19.470 --> 34:20.500
I don't understand.

34:22.100 --> 34:23.870
Why choose a love

34:23.870 --> 34:25.750
that is bound to be thorny?

34:27.620 --> 34:28.950
Can it truly bring happiness?

34:32.500 --> 34:33.950
When you meet that person,

34:36.660 --> 34:37.540
you will understand.

34:41.830 --> 34:42.830
May I ask

34:44.310 --> 34:45.390
which house you're from?

34:47.220 --> 34:48.390
I was born to a humble family.

34:48.950 --> 34:50.060
I'm not from any house.

34:51.310 --> 34:52.310
My name is Fang Ji;

34:53.126 --> 34:54.192
my courtesy name is Xianye.

35:17.430 --> 35:18.950
How did you know Jingyuan

35:18.950 --> 35:19.830
was in danger?

35:21.500 --> 35:22.990
After I left the Prophet's Mansion,

35:23.350 --> 35:25.060
I suddenly sensed your sister's aura.

35:25.660 --> 35:26.500
I realized

35:26.500 --> 35:27.470
she'd never go there,

35:27.990 --> 35:29.100
so I went to have a look.

35:29.790 --> 35:30.790
Just then, I saw

35:31.390 --> 35:32.790
Wang Qi forcing himself on her.

35:33.500 --> 35:34.830
I have dealt with Wang Qi.

35:35.020 --> 35:35.860
Simu,

35:36.620 --> 35:37.540
thank you for today.

35:41.470 --> 35:42.310
Do you like it?

35:43.700 --> 35:44.540
I do.

35:47.270 --> 35:48.110
So much

35:49.993 --> 35:51.232
that I don't want to leave you.

35:54.350 --> 35:55.790
I was just about to say goodbye.

35:56.580 --> 35:57.653
I'm going back to the Void.

35:59.060 --> 36:00.270
I have been away for too long.

36:00.900 --> 36:01.750
There are matters

36:01.750 --> 36:02.790
waiting for me to handle.

36:07.650 --> 36:09.396
Your sister-in-law
just learned who you are,

36:10.950 --> 36:12.060
and you leave this mess

36:12.830 --> 36:13.670
to me?

36:15.750 --> 36:16.950
I have a feeling

36:16.950 --> 36:18.310
I will be alone for years to come.

36:21.470 --> 36:22.910
I'm not good at comforting people.

36:26.580 --> 36:27.420
True.

36:27.870 --> 36:29.060
When you're not acting mortal,

36:30.470 --> 36:32.056
it's good enough
if you don't scare me.

36:33.950 --> 36:35.220
Why didn't I scare you off?

36:36.540 --> 36:37.380
I'm indeed leaving.

36:37.990 --> 36:38.910
In a few days, I'll go

36:39.830 --> 36:40.670
to gather troops.

36:40.910 --> 36:41.870
Where will you go?

36:42.310 --> 36:43.150
Have you decided yet?

36:43.620 --> 36:44.460
What?

36:44.790 --> 36:45.630
Do you know a place?

36:51.500 --> 36:52.350
Shenzhou.

36:53.220 --> 36:54.830
The people of Shenzhou are fierce.

36:54.830 --> 36:55.790
They act overbearing.

36:56.390 --> 36:57.750
Between families and villages,

36:57.750 --> 36:58.830
conflicts break out easily.

36:59.350 --> 37:00.470
For generations,

37:00.870 --> 37:01.763
a feud has never ended.

37:05.430 --> 37:06.270
Sounds promising.

37:08.620 --> 37:09.460
When do you leave?

37:11.500 --> 37:12.340
In about three days.

37:15.270 --> 37:16.110
Simu, stay with me

37:16.470 --> 37:17.430
for three more days.

37:17.450 --> 37:22.880
♪Though apart, my thoughts still swirl♪

37:24.060 --> 37:24.900
All right.

37:26.760 --> 37:29.120
♪For a name to be remembered♪

37:29.650 --> 37:33.010
♪There are passions and pains♪

37:33.210 --> 37:36.110
♪Hope we'll experience them together♪

37:37.890 --> 37:38.760
In 100 years

37:38.770 --> 37:39.650
after I die,

37:40.350 --> 37:41.580
you won't fall for anyone else.

37:44.270 --> 37:45.470
Because you'll never find

37:46.750 --> 37:48.390
another madman like me.

37:50.360 --> 37:51.382
Will I be able to find one

37:51.393 --> 37:52.220
after 100 years?

37:52.240 --> 37:53.670
♪I care for no one but you♪

37:53.910 --> 37:54.750
No.

37:56.750 --> 37:57.750
But you'll forget me.

37:58.830 --> 38:00.560
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

38:00.580 --> 38:02.180
You'll point to my grave and say,

38:04.100 --> 38:05.140
"I once truly cared"

38:05.140 --> 38:05.980
"for this person."

38:06.870 --> 38:10.480
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

38:10.500 --> 38:11.580
"But now,"

38:17.390 --> 38:18.660
"I can't even recall his name."

38:27.910 --> 38:28.750
Simu,

38:32.390 --> 38:33.620
remember me a little longer.

38:34.000 --> 38:36.080
♪My thoughts still swirl♪

38:38.758 --> 38:40.308
Remember me for another hundred years.

38:40.360 --> 38:42.620
♪For a name to be remembered♪

38:43.240 --> 38:46.770
♪There are passions and pains♪

38:46.770 --> 38:49.550
♪Hope we'll experience them together♪

38:50.270 --> 38:55.360
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

38:55.540 --> 38:57.450
♪Even if the day gives way to night♪

38:58.390 --> 38:59.230
Duan Shunxi,

39:00.310 --> 39:02.060
you've gotten so good
at playing pitiful.

39:02.400 --> 39:03.860
♪I care for no one but you♪

39:03.860 --> 39:05.060
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

39:05.060 --> 39:05.900
You saw through me.

39:05.900 --> 39:08.640
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

39:09.110 --> 39:10.290
♪Miracles♪

39:10.290 --> 39:11.840
♪Eternity, and radiance♪

39:11.840 --> 39:14.490
♪Worth more than any barren land♪

39:14.750 --> 39:17.220
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

39:17.220 --> 39:21.210
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

39:38.361 --> 39:43.691
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

39:44.021 --> 39:48.271
♪Light encountered shadow♪

39:49.631 --> 39:55.001
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

39:55.301 --> 39:59.901
♪The unbreakable fate♪

40:00.991 --> 40:02.831
♪Suddenly cracked♪

40:15.041 --> 40:20.481
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

40:20.661 --> 40:24.991
♪Light encountered shadow♪

40:26.361 --> 40:31.751
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

40:31.981 --> 40:35.921
♪The unbreakable fate♪

40:37.691 --> 40:39.581
♪Suddenly cracked♪

40:42.241 --> 40:45.401
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

40:45.401 --> 40:47.931
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

40:47.931 --> 40:53.451
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

40:53.451 --> 40:56.691
♪Following fate's guidance♪

40:56.691 --> 41:01.551
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

41:01.891 --> 41:04.911
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

41:04.911 --> 41:07.731
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

41:07.991 --> 41:10.521
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

41:10.521 --> 41:15.941
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

41:16.111 --> 41:19.181
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

41:19.341 --> 41:24.241
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

41:24.451 --> 41:27.921
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
